Definition: characterized by care and perseverance in carrying out tasks
Example: a diligent detective investigates all clues; a diligent search of the files
Synonyms: noun, attribute, diligence, NEGLIGENT, BUSY, CAREFUL, characterized, by, care, and, perseverance, in, carrying, out, tasks, a, diligent, detective, investigates, all, clues, search, of, the, files
Category: adj.all
